<P><HI>VOTED,</HI></P>
<P>That the Rt. Wor&s;hipful <HI>BENJAMIN HODGES,</HI> Ma&s;ter, <HI>ABEL LAWRENCE</HI> and <HI>EDWARD LANG,</HI> Brethren, be a Committee to wait on the Rev. Brother <HI>WILLIAM BENTLEY,</HI> with the thanks of this Lodge, for his Addre&s;s delivered in the Lodge this day, and to reque&s;t a copy for the pre&s;s.</P>
